profile_positions.description:
Projects:
- Conducting a water governance analysis in Colombia;
- Conducting a quick water governance scan on Indonesia; 
- Producing cooperation assessments and project proposals for international water governance projects;
- Contributing to projects in Colombia, Brazil, Bangladesh;
- Facilitating a national water governance dialogue in Colombia; 
- Contributing to the formulation of an international strategy for the WGC;
- Contributing to publications on water governance. I wrote for instance the chapter on Public Participation for the book "Building Blocks for Good Water Governance"
